{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10111270031367-1":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10111270031367-1","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000673226","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100149016218-1"],"books":null,"booksNew":null,"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":3,"description":"阅读课外文章，回答问题","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":720,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>祁黄羊</strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">春秋时代，晋国国君悼公任命祁黄羊担任中军尉，负责统领驾驭战车的士兵。几年后，祁黄羊告老退休，请求晋悼公准许。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">悼公说：“中军尉职责重大，你觉得谁能替代你呢？”“我看解狐就很不错。”祁黄羊想了想，郑重地说。悼公深感意外，说：“解狐不是你的仇人吗？你怎么会举荐他呢？”“主公问我谁可以担此重任，并没有问他是不是我的仇人哪！”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">悼公立即派使者去召解狐，没想到解狐大病在身，卧床不起，不久就去世了。悼公只好让祁黄羊再举荐一位能接替他的人。“看来只有祁午能担当此任了。”祁黄羊想了想，又郑重地说。悼公十分惊讶：“祁午不是你的儿子吗？”“事关国家安危，我不能不慎重。我只是想，朝中的人哪个有军事才能，可以担此重任，我压根儿就没去想他是不是我的仇人或亲人。”悼公于是决定由祁午继任中军尉。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">当时的人都很钦佩祁黄羊，说他外举不避仇，内举不避亲，做事如此出以公心，真是难得！</p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"祁黄羊先推荐了__$$__，是他的__$$__，后推荐了__$$__，是他的__$$__。","answers":[{"answer":"解狐","subAnswers":["解狐"],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null},{"answer":"仇人","subAnswers":["仇人"],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null},{"answer":"祁午","subAnswers":["祁午"],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null},{"answer":"儿子","subAnsw